---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Contato | Instituto Saber Global" currentPage="contato">

<!-- Section 1: Hero & Contatos -->
<section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-24 pb-16 md:pt-48 md:pb-32 px-6 bg-surface">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="z-10 relative text-center lg:text-left">
        <span data-animate="fade-right" class="inline-block text-tertiary font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase mb-4">
          Atendimento Exclusivo
        </span>
        <h1 data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 100ms;" class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-on-surface tracking-tighter leading-[1.1] mb-8">
          Estamos prontos para orientar sua jornada acadêmica.
        </h1>
        <p data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 200ms;" class="text-on-surface-variant text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12 max-w-lg mx-auto lg:mx-0 text-center md:text-justify">
          Escolha o canal de sua preferência e fale com nossa equipe de consultores especializados em educação internacional e formação continuada.
        </p>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-6" data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 350ms;">
          <a href="https://wa.me/5585999990000" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-6 rounded-[1.5rem] transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 active:scale-[0.98] cursor-pointer hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-green-500/10 group border border-outline-variant/10 block">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-500/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-green-500 transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors text-3xl">chat_bubble</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-extrabold text-on-surface mb-1">WhatsApp</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Atendimento ágil para matrículas e editais.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="#formulario" class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-6 rounded-[1.5rem] transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 active:scale-[0.98] cursor-pointer hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/10 group border border-outline-variant/10 block">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-fixed rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary-fixed group-hover:text-white transition-colors text-3xl">mail</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-extrabold text-on-surface mb-1">E-mail</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Envio de documentação e novas parcerias.</p>
          </a>
          <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-6 rounded-[1.5rem] transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 active:scale-[0.98] cursor-pointer hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-tertiary/10 group border border-outline-variant/10">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-tertiary-fixed rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-tertiary transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-tertiary-fixed group-hover:text-white transition-colors text-3xl">call</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-extrabold text-on-surface mb-1">Telefone Fixo</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">(85) 3000-0000</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-6 rounded-[1.5rem] transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 active:scale-[0.98] cursor-pointer hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-secondary/10 group border border-outline-variant/10">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary-fixed rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-secondary transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-secondary-fixed group-hover:text-white transition-colors text-3xl">location_on</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-extrabold text-on-surface mb-1">Endereço</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Fortaleza, Ceará (Sede Admin).</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative hidden lg:block" data-animate="zoom-in" style="transition-delay: 400ms;">
        <div class="absolute -top-12 -left-12 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10 animate-pulse"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-12 -right-12 w-[350px] h-[350px] bg-secondary/15 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10"></div>
        <div class="relative rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden perspective-img shadow-2xl shadow-primary/20">
